2026-05-13T17:40:35.8704978Z 22    <!--
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8705871Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8706660Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8707360Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8708171Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8708961Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8710256Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8711171Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8712069Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8712943Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8713766Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8714423Z 33    -->
2026-05-13T17:40:35.8715116Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
